OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said in September that
OL,7,Fnurses could take strike action by
OL,8,FNovember if a #200 million funding gap
OL,9,Fis not bridged to meet the recommended
OL,10,Fpay increase.
OL,12,FMr O'Dowd told MLAs on Monday that the
OL,13,FUK Government has been "failing to
OL,14,Fprovide sufficient funding for public
OL,15,Fservices".
OL,17,FHe said: "They should not be in the
OL,18,Fposition of having to consider strike
OL,19,Faction to get pay awards that they are
OL,20,Fentitled to.
OL,26,@uD@XOUwD@IO]yD@JOU
