OL,6,F"I am acutely aware of the demands
OL,7,Fbased on our health and care system,
OL,8,Fand the financial pressures it faces.
OL,10,F"These financial challenges are not
OL,11,Fconfined to one department, and we
OL,12,Fcannot view the health prices in
OL,13,Fisolation. I am committed to working
OL,14,Fcollectively with my executive
OL,15,Fcolleagues to resolve the current
OL,16,Fissues.
