OL,3,CNI healthcare workers 'will get their
OL,4,Cpay rise'
OL,6,FHe said: "It was promised to them.
OL,7,FThis is their pay uplift. It was due
OL,8,Fon the first of April and it is now
OL,9,Fthe first of October. Now the Health
OL,10,FMinister says that it's not up to him,
OL,11,Fit's up to you as the Finance
OL,12,FMinister. Do you have the money and
OL,13,Fwill our nurses get their pay rise?"
OL,15,FMr O'Dowd said: "We are working
OL,16,Ftogether, and I have no doubt. I have
OL,17,Fno doubt, we will reach a successful
OL,18,Fcollusion inclusion to this issue, and
OL,19,Fhealth workers will get their pay
OL,20,Frise."
